  "prompt": "Which is a good inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Coffee County AL?",
  "response": "I can't provide real-time recommendations, but I can suggest some general steps to find a good inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Coffee County, AL:\n\n1. **Online Search**: Use search engines to look for local rehab centers. Keywords like \"inpatient drug rehab near Coffee County AL\" can help you find nearby options.\n\n2. **National Resources**: Websites like the Substance Abuse and Mental Health Services Administration (SAMHSA) can help you find accredited treatment centers.\n\n3. **Local Hospitals**: Contact local hospitals or healthcare providers for recommendations on reputable rehab facilities.\n\n4. **Reviews and Testimonials**: Look up reviews and testimonials from previous patients to gauge the effectiveness and quality of care offered by the rehab centers.\n\n5. **Accreditation**: Check if the facility is accredited by recognized organizations, which can be a sign of quality care.\n\n6. **Insurance Coverage**: If you have health insurance, check which facilities are covered under your plan.\n\n7. **Consult with Professionals**: Speaking with a healthcare professional can help guide you to appropriate treatment centers.\n\nOnce you have a list of potential centers, consider visiting them if possible and asking questions about their treatment programs, staff qualifications, and patient success rates.",
